result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :visible="visible"
  :keyboard="false"
  :maskClosable="false"
  okText="保存"
  okType="primary"
  @ok="handleOk()"
  @cancel="handleCancel()">
  <a-form
    :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="日期"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-date-picker
        style="width:100%"
        v-decorator="[
              'patrol_date',
              {rules: [{type: 'object', required: true, message: '请输入日期'}],
            initialValue: record ? record.patrol_date : null}
            ]"></a-date-picker>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="施工安全生产"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'security_production',
          {
            rules:[
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.security_production : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="安全设施配备"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'security_facilities',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.security_facilities : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="安全隐患"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
        'security_hidden_danger',
        {
          rules: [
            { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
          ],
          validateTrigger: 'blur',
          initialValue: record ? record.security_hidden_danger : null
        }
      ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="前期问题整改"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'previous_problems',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个字符以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.previous_problems : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="检查人"
      v-bind="layout">
     <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'inspector',
          {
            rules: [
             { required: true, message: '请输入检查人' },
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个字符以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.inspector : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
</a-modal>
